{"tid":2236128,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"宣道校友轟教局顛倒是非  逾兩萬人發信撐釘牌教師","createTime":"2020-10-09T08:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T09:01:18.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"19f8097bbd33fd5afb0e4de963b8f3370543ce32","tid":2236128,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/KVT7RQPRKBAEZALGGUXYNUP6KI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FKVT7RQPRKBAEZALGGUXYNUP6KI%2F&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzs22uFAamDTqma2v4g3iiws%3D&h=b1a0a0dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2FKVT7RQPRKBAEZALGGUXYNUP6KI%2F&h=0c971929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/KVT7RQPRKBAEZALGGUXYNUP6KI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n宣道校友轟教局顛倒是非 <br />\n逾兩萬人發信撐釘牌教師<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】九龍塘宣道小學一名教師因製作教材討論言論自由，被教育局扣上「有計劃地散播港獨訊息」帽子，終身剝奪其教師資格，引發社會公憤。數百名宣道校友及家長發表聯署聲明，批評當局顛倒是非、罔顧學生利益。公眾擔心涉事教師生計受影響，紛紛伸出援手，不過該教師表示沒有尋找上門補習工作的需要。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：舊生登報聲援：不因毀謗驚惶<br />\n<br />\n一群宣道校友及家長昨發表聯署聲明，以「顛倒是非教育局罔顧學生利益 擇善固執眾校友力撐老師清白」為題，聲援被釘牌教師。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/I6F4rXU8XdUnDh_hK7cfjWSo960=/855x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LK3GTKWN6RCXXAUSSPLYGUTH5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FI6F4rXU8XdUnDh_hK7cfjWSo960%3D%2F855x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLK3GTKWN6RCXXAUSSPLYGUTH5I.jpg&h=896a3557&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■教育野前日發起一人一信聲援涉事教師。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事主澄清毋須找補習工作<br />\n<br />\n聲明批評當局的調查欠透明度，不但未正式召開紀律聆訊，以予老師公平、透明的申辯渠道，更未附上書面報告，以提供充份理由佐證對老師專業失德甚至傷害學生的指控。校方早已應教育局要求進行兩次調查，結果均為投訴內容不成立，教育局卻政治立場先行，推翻校方的調查結果，手法不但有違程序公義，更是對校方專業、校本管理的侮辱。<br />\n<br />\n聯署校友及家長指出，相關教師任教逾二十年，一向深受學生及同事愛戴，默默貢獻。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n學生組織教育野前日發起的《要求教育局撤回取消教師註冊決定》一人一信行動，至昨日傍晚已有超過二萬人參與，包括近500名宣道家長、學生及校友。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n涉事教師終身不能執教，事業大受影響。社交平台流傳他「急需尋找上門補習工作」，不過教協昨日在facebook引述教師表示：「感謝各位的關心和支持，但現時我並無需要尋找上門補習的工作，謝謝大家！」教協副會長、教育界立法會議員葉建源表示，該老師現時都面對一定壓力，教協會全力協助他就教育局的決定上訴，若有需要亦會協助入稟法院司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uVcz5IzZAseTK2P9v9KJulrpWwk=/849x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PVAYLHQESBC7NNL37HFXJNUICE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuVcz5IzZAseTK2P9v9KJulrpWwk%3D%2F849x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPVAYLHQESBC7NNL37HFXJNUICE.jpg&h=5022cb3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■教協為涉事教師眾籌生活費及上訴費用。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/MdGUVvENWU5agTF9HiLXJxfwEJE=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4PL7KQ5OJFDBRIH6IYKZNIWEHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FMdGUVvENWU5agTF9HiLXJxfwEJE%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4PL7KQ5OJFDBRIH6IYKZNIWEHI.jpg&h=c0d21090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■宣道小學一名教師被指「宣揚港獨」遭終身釘牌，引起社會關注。資料圖片"},{"pid":"1a20ea9ba4417d752b12b607c2fcc1719af50296","tid":2236128,"uid":219564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T09:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}